obal_Objects/Object/valueOf\"><code>Object.prototype.valueOf()</code></a></li></ol></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p><strong><code>getSeconds()</code></strong> メソッドは、地方時に基づき、指定した日時の「秒」を返します。</p>\n\n<div id=\"sect2\"><iframe class=\"interactive\" height=\"490\" src=\"https://interactive-examples.mdn.mozilla.net/pages/js/date-getseconds.html\" title=\"MDN Web Docs Interactive Example\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"構文","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><var>dateObj</var>.getSeconds()</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"return_value","title":"返値","isH3":true,"content":"<p>地方時に基づき、与えた日付の「秒」を表す 0 から 59 までの間の整数値。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"examples","title":"例","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"using_getseconds","title":"getSeconds() の使用","isH3":true,"content":"<p>以下の 2 行目の文は、<a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date\"><code>Date</code></a> オブジェクト <code>Xmas95</code> の値に基づき、変数 <code>seconds</code> に 30 という値を代入します。</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> Xmas95 <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Date</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'December 25, 1995 23:15:30'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> seconds <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> Xmas95<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getSeconds</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>seconds<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 30</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"仕様書","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">仕様書</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://tc39.es/ecma262/#sec-date.prototype.getseconds\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ECMAScript (ECMA-262)<br><small lang=\"ja\">Date.prototype.getSeconds の定義</small></a></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"javascript.builtins.Date.getSeconds","dataURL":"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/getSeconds/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"関連情報","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/getUTCSeconds\"><code>Date.prototype.getUTCSeconds()</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/setSeconds\"><code>Date.prototype.setSeconds()</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"構文","id":"syntax"},{"text":"例","id":"examples"},{"text":"仕様書","id":"specifications"},{"text":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"関連情報","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"getSeconds() メソッドは、地方時に基づき、指定した日時の「秒」を返します。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Date.prototype.getSeconds()","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"Date.prototype.getSeconds()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Date.prototype.getSeconds()","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Date.prototype.getSeconds()","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Date.pr